{"id": "c80", "problem": "0961_B", "label": "O(n)", "code": "n,k=map(int,input().split())\na=list(map(int,input().split()))\nt=list(map(int,input().split()))\nans=0\nm=0\nfor i in range(n):\n    if t[i]:\n        ans+=a[i]\n        a[i]=0\ncf=[0]*(n+1)\nfor i in range(1,n+1):\n    cf[i]=cf[i-1]+a[i-1]\nfor i in range(n-k+1):\n    m=max(m,cf[i+k]-cf[i])\nprint(ans+m)"}
