{"id": "c95", "problem": "0999_D", "label": "O(n)", "code": "n,m=map(int, input().split())\na=list(map(int, input().split()))\nt=n//m\nremain=[[] for i in range(m)]\nfor i in range(n):\n    x=a[i]%m\n    remain[x].append(i)\nans=0\nf=[]\nfor i in range(2*m):\n    cur=i%m\n    while len(remain[cur])>t:\n        elm=remain[cur].pop()\n        f.append([elm,i])\n    while len(remain[cur])<t and len(f)!=0:\n        elm,j=f.pop()\n        remain[cur].append(elm)\n        a[elm]+=abs(i-j)\n        ans+=abs(i-j)\nprint(ans)\nprint(*a)\n"}
