{"id": "c97", "problem": "1000_B", "label": "O(n)", "code": "n,M=map(int,input().split())\na=[0]+[int(x) for x in input().split()]+[M]\n\nt1=[]\nt2=[]\nfor i in range(n+1):\n    if i%2==0:\n        t1.append(a[i+1]-a[i])\n    else:\n        t2.append(a[i+1]-a[i])\nt2.append(0)\n\nimport math\nans=sum(t1)\np=0\nq=sum(t2)\nfor i in range(math.ceil(n/2)):\n    p=p+t1[i]\n    q=q-t2[i-1]\n    ans=max(ans,p+q-1)\nprint(ans)\n"}
